readable.content: A boy high in the air above the dirt and water near the red rock cliffs . A medium sized child jumps off of a dusty bank over a creek . a young person wearing a grey shirt and yellow shorts jumping into a river . Person in yellow shorts , grey shirt with logo jumping from bank into the water . The boy in yellow shorts leaps from river bank towards the river .
